		"description": "Complete API collection for TrackMyGrade - Student Grade Management System.\n\n## Getting Started\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Import the environment file (TrackMyGradeAPI.postman_environment.json)\n3. Start the API: Run TrackMyGradeAPI.exe or use start-api.ps1\n4. Run the requests in order:\n   - First register a teacher\n   - The teacherId will be saved automatically\n   - Then test student CRUD operations\n\n## Authentication\nThe API uses a simple teacher ID header for authentication:\n- Header: `X-TeacherId`\n- Value: Teacher ID from registration/login response\n- This is automatically set after registration/login",
